## Conclusion

This first batch of hymns only came out recently, but we're starting to see some trends already. Again, this is only based on 582 sacrament meetings from 209 wards. It's not an insignificant amount of data, but it is just a sliver of the many wards across the country and the world. As always, I'm collecting more data and if you'd like to contribute your ward's data, you can do so [here](/contribute.html).
